title: File:Durban, South Africa by Planet Labs.jpg
author: Planet Labs, Inc.
description:
Durban South Africa July 18, 2016
  • Durban, with its popular beach spot, the Golden Mile, attracts throngs of tourists. 1.45 million visited the city and nearby attractions over the course of 45 days last summer. Moses Mabhida Stadium, visible just behind the beach, played host to several games of the 2010 World Cup.
